This is QuikWiki

* View the HomePage

  '''http://''server_name''/quikwiki/quikwiki.cgi/?HomePage'''  

* Shortcut for above

  '''http://''server_name''/quikwiki/quikwiki.cgi/?'''

* View a page named ''MyPage,'' or create it if it doesn't exist.

  '''http://''server_name''/quikwiki/quikwiki.cgi/?MyPage'''


* Edit ''MyPage.''

   '''http//''server_name''/quikwiki/quikwiki.cgi/?MyPage&action=edit'''


* Text markup is similar to WikiWiki, with ''emphasized (italic),'' '''bold,''' and,

 preformatted

text.

* Click on the '''Edit''' link above to view the markup tags.

  use '''http://''server_name''/quikwiki/quikwiki.cgi?QuikWiki&action=edit'''

to view the markup tags.

* JPEG and GIF images are displayed in-line.

* Page templates with embedded Perl scripts.  The files '''WikiHeader,'''
'''WikiFooter,''' and '''ODBC''' are examples.

* Click on the '''Doc''' link above to view the manual.
